 It was quite nice giving it with sandblast.

00:02:54.540 --> 00:02:55.380
 - Amazing.

00:02:55.380 --> 00:02:56.200
 - Yeah.

00:02:56.200 --> 00:02:57.540
 - And giving it, they were at sea.

